  "epitaph": "Here lies the framework that promised to write as one,\nSynchronizing cursors before the work was done.\nA starry dawn in April, a silent September breath,\nNow the conflict resolution sleeps the sleep of death.\nYour collaborative dream hangs in the branches, still,\nA ghost within the memory of the commits we had will.\nRest in /dev/null.",
